      "html": "<figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2024/01/T-ng-Ngay-10-000-VNST_ENG-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1011\" srcset=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w600/2024/01/T-ng-Ngay-10-000-VNST_ENG-1.png 600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1000/2024/01/T-ng-Ngay-10-000-VNST_ENG-1.png 1000w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1600/2024/01/T-ng-Ngay-10-000-VNST_ENG-1.png 1600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2024/01/T-ng-Ngay-10-000-VNST_ENG-1.png 1800w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p><em>Accompanying Nami users in experiencing the new feature, Nami Membership, the first 1000 users to utilize the benefits of the Membership feature will receive a direct reward of 10,000 VNST.</em></p><p>Nami Exchange recently introduced the Membership feature, allowing users to enjoy discounts when purchasing goods and services from Nami's partners across various industries such as dining, shopping, beauty, travel, and more...</p><p>Find detailed instructions on how to use Nami Membership <a href=\"https://nami.exchange/support/faq/huong-dan-chung/huong-dan-su-dung-tinh-nang-nami-membership?ref=blog.vnst.io\">here.</a></p><h3 id=\"how-to-receive-10000-vnst\">How to receive 10,000 VNST</h3><p>To receive 10,000 VNST, users can follow these steps:</p><ul><li>Step 1: Create an account on Nami Exchange and complete the identity verification process (KYC).</li><li>Step 2: Access the Nami Membership feature.</li><li>Step 3: View the list of offered services and obtain a QR code.</li><li>Step 4: Visit a participating store and scan the QR code to receive discounts during payment.</li><li>Step 5: Receive 10,000 VNST directly into the Spot wallet for the first QR code usage within 5 minutes after payment.</li></ul><h3 id=\"receive-additional-vnst-from-namis-tet-2024-event-series\">Receive additional VNST from Nami's Tet 2024 event series</h3><p>Users have the opportunity to receive additional VNST in Nami's highly attractive Tet events, where VNST is a companion:</p><ul><li>New Year's Race: Participate in the \"LUCKY NEW YEAR HARVEST\" mini-game during the livestream to win attractive rewards, with a chance to receive up to 300,000 VNST.</li><li>NAO Futures Season 12: Join the Nami Championship Tournament with prizes of up to 2,000,000,000 VNST.</li></ul><h3 id=\"about-vnst\">About VNST</h3><p>VNST is a decentralized stablecoin, demonstrating transparency through on-chain data and backed by the stability of the most reputable stablecoins worldwide. Committed to providing diverse and convenient choices in the Web3 space, VNST promises to be a safe and efficient financial tool, serving the user community in the Web3 field in Vietnam and globally.</p><p>Don't forget to follow our channels to stay updated with the latest information from the event!</p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/vnstcoin?ref=blog.vnst.io\">X</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VNST.io/\">Facebook </a>| <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstann?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Announcements</a> |  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/pwRwbcHHkK?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Discord</a> | <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstgroup?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Discussion</a><br><br></p>",
