      "html": "<figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2024/01/Nami-Championship-tr--th--ng-qua-VNST_ENG--1--2.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1011\" srcset=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w600/2024/01/Nami-Championship-tr--th--ng-qua-VNST_ENG--1--2.png 600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1000/2024/01/Nami-Championship-tr--th--ng-qua-VNST_ENG--1--2.png 1000w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1600/2024/01/Nami-Championship-tr--th--ng-qua-VNST_ENG--1--2.png 1600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2024/01/Nami-Championship-tr--th--ng-qua-VNST_ENG--1--2.png 1800w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p><em>We are delighted to collaborate with Nami Exchange to reward outstanding users in the Nami Championship - Nao Futures Season 12, one of the most anticipated events during this Lunar New Year.</em></p><h3 id=\"nami-championshipnao-futures-season-12\">Nami Championship - Nao Futures Season 12</h3><p>The Nami Championship organized by Nami Exchange is an exciting event within the community, where participants have the opportunity to receive rewards directly in VNST. With an attractive prize pool of up to 2,000,000,000 VNST, participants have the chance not only to earn profits but also to actively contribute to the development and value appreciation of VNST in the market. The competition is an excellent opportunity to stimulate and promote interest and trading activities of VNST within the Nami community.</p><ul><li>Time: 00:00 January 15th - 00:00 on February 19th, 2024 (UTC+7).</li><li>Participants: Individuals or Community Partners.</li></ul><p>Follow the latest information about the tournament <a href=\"https://nao.namifutures.com/contest?ref=blog.vnst.io\">here</a></p><h3 id=\"vnst-accompanies-the-nami-community\">VNST accompanies the Nami community</h3><p>To enhance development and connection with community, we are collaborating with Nami in a series of events welcoming the new year 2024:</p><ul><li>Cross-Tet Racing: Join the mini-game \"Lunar New Year Harvest\" in the livestream to receive attractive rewards, with a chance to receive up to 300,000 VNST.</li><li>Program \"Welcoming the New Year - Get Great Deals\": Specially dedicated to the first 1,000 people using the QR Code from Nami Membership with a 10,000 VNST discount.</li></ul><p>We believe that this event series will bring unique experiences to users and contribute to creating a positive trading environment within the community.</p><h3 id=\"about-vnst\">About VNST</h3><p>VNST is a decentralized stablecoin, demonstrating transparency through on-chain data and backed by the stability of the most reputable stablecoins worldwide. Committed to providing diverse and convenient choices in the Web3 space, VNST promises to be a safe and efficient financial tool, serving the user community in the Web3 field in Vietnam and globally.</p><p>Don't forget to follow our channels to stay updated with the latest information from the Nami Championship - Nao Futures Season 12 tournament!</p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/vnstcoin?ref=blog.vnst.io\">X</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VNST.io/\">Facebook </a>| <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstann?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Announcements</a> |  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/pwRwbcHHkK?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Discord</a> | <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstgroup?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Discussion</a></p>",
