      "html": "<figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/12/VNST-sponsors-workshop-series_-Solana-Consumer-Hack-12_Done-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"674\" srcset=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w600/2023/12/VNST-sponsors-workshop-series_-Solana-Consumer-Hack-12_Done-1.png 600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1000/2023/12/VNST-sponsors-workshop-series_-Solana-Consumer-Hack-12_Done-1.png 1000w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/12/VNST-sponsors-workshop-series_-Solana-Consumer-Hack-12_Done-1.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>VNST accompanies SCI Labs and Solana Superteam Vietnam in efforts to promote the development of blockchain technology in Vietnam, to nurture and support young talents in developing their own creativity and delivering unique technological solutions.</p><h2 id=\"solana-consumer-hack-12\">Solana Consumer Hack 12</h2><p>Solana Consumer Hack 12 is a blockchain product-programming competition designated for young talents who possess solid foundations in the field of blockchain technology. This is an opportunity to test their own ability, develop new ideas and create useful solutions.</p><h2 id=\"solana-consumer-hack-12-workshop-series\">Solana Consumer Hack 12 workshop series</h2><p>The Workshop series is designed for everyone who wants to learn about Web3 and blockchain. A special feature is the presence of leading experts and influential guests in the market. They not only shared extensive knowledge but also brought valuable practical experiences through 5 workshops:</p><p>The first 2 Workshops are open to all participants</p><p>The next 3 Workshops focus on programming languages ​​and the necessary knowledge to participate in the hackathon.</p><h2 id=\"vnst-in-the-solana-consumer-hack-12-workshop-series\">VNST in the Solana Consumer Hack 12 workshop series</h2><p>As an Associate Partner, VNST finance the workshops to support the organizers and contestants in achieving the core goals of the program: encouraging creativity and building a healthy competitive environment.</p><p>Accompanying reputable organizations to create effective and practical activities will contribute to realizing VNST's mission: Providing safe, stable and convenient financial solutions for users, Helps users easily enter the financial technology market.</p><h2 id=\"about-vnst\">About VNST</h2><p>VNST is a decentralized stablecoin with transparent on-chain data, guaranteed by the stable value of the most popular and reputable stablecoins in the global crypto asset market.</p><p>The stablecoins that ensure value for VNST have transaction volume and stability proven over a long period of time, are issued by reputable organizations with proven potential, and are periodically audited. VNST will be a safe, reliable solution, providing diverse and convenient choices and expanding future applications for users in the Web3 field in Vietnam and around the world</p>",
