      "title": "VNST: OFFICIAL SPONSOR FOR WINTER IDEATHON",
      "slug": "vnst-official-sponsor-for-winter-ideathon",
      "html": "<figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/11/Winter-Ideathon_Done-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1011\" srcset=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w600/2023/11/Winter-Ideathon_Done-1.png 600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1000/2023/11/Winter-Ideathon_Done-1.png 1000w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1600/2023/11/Winter-Ideathon_Done-1.png 1600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/11/Winter-Ideathon_Done-1.png 1800w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>VNST is honored to announce that we have become the official sponsor of the Winter Ideathon event, organized by Web3 Space. This marks a significant milestone in the collaboration between VNST, the first decentralized stablecoin in Vietnam, and the blockchain community in Vietnam.</p><h2 id=\"what-is-the-winter-ideathon\">What is the Winter Ideathon?</h2><p>The Winter Ideathon is an exciting competition organized by Web3 Space. This unique event aims to encourage creativity and generate new ideas in the field of Web3. Whether participants are experienced developers, tech enthusiasts, or simply individuals passionate about innovation, this Ideathon provides the perfect opportunity to showcase skills and contribute to the development of Web3 technology.</p><p>With the desire to create an environment that encourages participants to come up with breakthrough ideas, Winter Ideathon at Web3 Space allows participants to utilize their creativity to develop products around the competition's themes, including DeFi, SocialFi &amp; GameFi, NFT &amp; RWA, and General DApps.</p><p>With VNST's vision of creating and maintaining a robust blockchain ecosystem, we believe that the Winter Ideathon will be an ideal platform to share ideas, learn, and build innovative blockchain applications. VNST looks forward to a successful event filled with new ideas and delivering core values to the Vietnamese Builder community.<br></p><h2 id=\"about-vnst\">About VNST</h2><p>VNST is a decentralized stablecoin with transparent on-chain data, guaranteed by the stable value of the most popular and reputable stablecoins in the global crypto asset market.</p><p>The stablecoins that ensure value for VNST have transaction volume and stability proven over a long period of time, are issued by reputable organizations with proven potential, and are periodically audited. VNST will be a safe, reliable solution, providing diverse and convenient choices and expanding future applications for users in the Web3 field in Vietnam and around the world.</p><p>| <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstann?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Announcements</a> |  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/pwRwbcHHkK?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Discord</a> | <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstgroup?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Discussion</a></p>",
