      "title": "Announcement of strategic partner Nami Exchange and time to integrate VNST on Nami Exchange",
      "slug": "announcing-strategic-partner-nami-exchange",
      "html": "<p><em>VNST officially announced strategic partner Nami Exchange, one of the first partners that will integrate the VNST stablecoin in the Beta phase.</em></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/09/Merchant-Nami--1-.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"674\" srcset=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w600/2023/09/Merchant-Nami--1-.png 600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1000/2023/09/Merchant-Nami--1-.png 1000w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/09/Merchant-Nami--1-.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>This partnership aims to provide Nami Exchange users with the earliest opportunity to experience a completely new stable coin, aiming for transparency with real-time on-chain data, convenient and promising transactions. brings many attractive benefits to users in the future.</p><p>The two sides highly appreciate this cooperation with the expectation of actively contributing to the next stages of development of the crypto asset market as well as the Web 3 field in Vietnam and around the world.</p><p>After completing the integration process between the two systems, Nami Exchange will list trading pairs with VNST currency on NAO Futures and Nami Futures products so that users can experience the Beta features of the stable VNST coins. This will help diversify the choices and experiences of Nami Exchange users besides the trading pairs that have been operating stably over the past time.</p><p>The time to integrate VNST onto Nami Exchange will be from 2023-09-09 09:00 (UTC)</p><blockquote><em>Disclaimer:</em></blockquote><blockquote><em>VNST reserves the right, at its sole discretion, to edit, change or cancel this notice at any time and for any reason without prior notice.</em></blockquote><blockquote><em>VNST is in the beta testing phase and has made adjustments to optimize operations and control risks, so users need to consider adverse factors during the testing process to make prudent management decisions. Manage assets within your risk tolerance with full awareness.</em></blockquote><h3 id=\"about-vnst\">About VNST</h3><p>VNST is a decentralized stablecoin with transparent on-chain data, guaranteed by the stable value of the most popular and reputable stable coins in the global crypto asset market. The stablecoins that ensure value for VNST have transaction volume and stability proven over a long period of time, issued by reputable organizations with proven potential and periodically audited. VNST will be a safe, reliable solution, providing diverse and convenient choices and expanding future applications for users in the Web3 field in Vietnam and around the world.</p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/vnstcoin?ref=blog.vnst.io\">X</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VNST.io/\">Facebook </a>| <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstann?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Announcements</a> |  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/pwRwbcHHkK?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Discord</a> | <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstgroup?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Discussion</a></p><h3 id=\"about-nami-exchange\">About Nami Exchange</h3><p>Nami Exchange is a flexible cryptocurrency trading and effective investment platform belonging to the Nami Foundation ecosystem, providing Spot and Futures trading products with nearly 700 trading pairs, supporting leverage up to x125, with a team of Professional support team operates 24/7</p><p><a href=\"https://nami.exchange/vi?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Website</a> |  <a href=\"https://nami.exchange/?shortlink=appblog&c=Blog&pid=Blog&af_xp=custom&source_caller=ui&ref=blog.vnst.io\">Application</a> | <a href=\"https://t.me/CongdongNamiVietnam?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Nami Vietnam Community</a> | <a href=\"https://t.me/NamiGlobalGroup?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Nami Global</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/namifutures\">Facebook Fanpage</a> |  <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/nami.exchange\">Facebook Nami Community</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/NamiExchange?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Twitter</a></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>",
