      "title": "Strategic partner announcement Oxalus and time of integrating VNST on Oxalus Wallet",
      "slug": "announcement-of-oxalus-and-vnst-cooperation-strategy",
      "html": "<blockquote>VNST is pleased to introduce the first business partner Oxalus Wallet - Including a social platform and a crypto wallet that has attracted more than 600,000 Web 3.0 users and successfully raised capital at the Seed round. to $1.1 million from Kyber Ventures and IDG Capital in May 2023.</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/09/Merchant-Oxalus-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"674\" srcset=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w600/2023/09/Merchant-Oxalus-1.png 600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1000/2023/09/Merchant-Oxalus-1.png 1000w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/09/Merchant-Oxalus-1.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>Through Oxalus Wallet (Available on CH Play for Android and Appstore for IOS), users can store and convert VNST to crypto assets safely, conveniently and quickly. In addition, users using VNST can fully access and trade NFTs through the Oxalus.io social commerce platform, thereby increasing the benefits of VNST stablecoin owners.</p><p>The cooperation between Oxalus and VNST promises to bring many new and interesting experiences to users. Those who own VNST early in the Beta phase on Oxalus Wallet will have the opportunity to participate in exclusive events and programs jointly organized by the two units in the near future. Open up new investment and trading opportunities in the NFT market with VNST.</p><p>The time to integrate VNST into Oxalus Wallet is expected to be from September 15, 2023. Please follow VNST and Oxalus Wallet channels for more detailed information!</p><p>Look forward to great things coming from this collaboration!</p><blockquote><em>*Disclaimer:</em></blockquote><blockquote><em>VNST reserves the right, at its sole discretion, to edit, change or cancel this notice at any time and for any reason without prior notice.</em></blockquote><blockquote><em>VNST is in the beta testing phase and has made adjustments to optimize operations and control risks, so users need to consider adverse factors during the testing process to make prudent management decisions. Manage assets within your risk tolerance with full awareness.</em></blockquote><h2 id=\"about-vnst\">About VNST</h2><p>VNST is a decentralized stablecoin with transparent on-chain data, guaranteed by the stable value of the most popular and reputable stable coins in the global crypto asset market. The stablecoins that ensure value for VNST have transaction volume and stability proven over a long period of time, issued by reputable organizations with proven potential and periodically audited. VNST will be a safe, reliable solution, providing diverse and convenient choices and expanding future applications for users in the Web3 field in Vietnam and around the world.</p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/vnstcoin?ref=blog.vnst.io\">X</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VNST.io/\">Facebook </a>| <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstann?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Announcements</a> |  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/pwRwbcHHkK?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Discord</a> | <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstgroup?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Discussion</a></p><h2 id=\"about-oxalus\"><strong>About Oxalus</strong></h2><p>Oxalus is an NFT aggregator, which aims to solve the problems of NFT trading platforms such as fragmentation of NFT marketplaces, or excessive gas fees. It is an NFT-focused social commerce platform with various utilities and applications. At Oxalus, users can fully follow major NFT investors through their Wallet, personal collection to make informed investment decisions.</p><p>In addition, Oxalus has developed the first NFT Game Wallet product called \"Oxalus Wallet '', users can view NFTs products in the game, ensure asset security, and fully control what you spend. own, and perform storage and transfer of multiple assets and tokens on many different chains.</p><p><a href=\"https://oxalus.io/?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Website</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Oxalus_io?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Twitter </a>| <a href=\"https://discord.gg/h4dBTGKxsC?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Discord</a> | <a href=\"https://t.me/OxalusAnnouncement?ref=blog.vnst.io\">TG Channel</a>| <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/vn/app/oxalus-nft-wallet/id1620111723?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Download OW on Appstore</a> | <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.oxalus.wallet&hl=en&gl=US&ref=blog.vnst.io\">Download OW on GG Play</a></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>",
