      "title": "VNST and the special number: 292023",
      "slug": "vnst-and-the-special-number-292023",
      "html": "<blockquote>In the anticipation and expectation of the VNST team, on September 2, 2023, the first Mint VNST command was executed, marking a significant turning point in VNST's journey.</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/09/9_ENG-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1041\" srcset=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w600/2023/09/9_ENG-1.png 600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1000/2023/09/9_ENG-1.png 1000w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1600/2023/09/9_ENG-1.png 1600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/09/9_ENG-1.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h2 id=\"number-292023\">Number \"292023\"</h2><p>Behind the sequence of numbers 292023 is an essential occasion in the VNST team's history. It is the moment when VNST, like a newborn, makes its first tentative steps into the world of cryptocurrencies.</p><p>On September 2, 2023, at exactly 0 hours (UTC+7), the first VNST tokens were created with tremendous optimism for a new journey, unlocking opportunities that were previously unimaginable. This is a substantial milestone in the VNST's journey. The first Mint VNST event is a declaration of VNST's existence, innovation, and significance.</p><h2 id=\"genesis-wallet\">Genesis Wallet</h2><p>The \"Genesis Wallet\" is more than an ordinary cryptocurrency wallet; it represents VNST's origins and innovation. It symbolizes the hopes of VNST's founders, who desired to create a unique and stable coin.</p><p>True to the meaning of \"Genesis\" - a magnificent beginning - the Genesis Wallet is a part of VNST's narrative in the world of cryptocurrencies, marking an adventure full of potential and an entirely fresh start for VNST. The initial amount of VNST tokens have been stored in the Genesis Wallet and completely sealed to honour this historic project, marking VNST's first step in allowing users access to applications, transactions, and future development.</p><p>Details of the first VNST transaction:<a href=\"https://bscscan.com/tx/0xacff3792c72db347a4bcbb4f3ad69c54ba1965c889ea2a030bbd350983997397?ref=blog.vnst.io\"> https://bscscan.com/tx/0xacff3792c72db347a4bcbb4f3ad69c54ba1965c889ea2a030bbd350983997397</a></p><h2 id=\"about-vnst\">About VNST</h2><p>VNST is a decentralized stablecoin with transparent on-chain data, guaranteed by the stable value of the most popular and reputable stable coins in the global crypto asset market. The stablecoins that ensure value for VNST have transaction volume and stability proven over a long period of time, issued by reputable organizations with proven potential and periodically audited. VNST will be a safe, reliable solution, providing diverse and convenient choices and expanding future applications for users in the Web3 field in Vietnam and around the world.</p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/vnstcoin?ref=blog.vnst.io\">X</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VNST.io/\">Facebook </a>| <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstann?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Announcements</a> |  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/pwRwbcHHkK?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Discord</a> | <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstgroup?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Discussion</a></p><p><strong>Details: </strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://whitepaper.vnst.io/vnst_whitepaper_en/table-of-contents/vnst-whitepaper?ref=blog.vnst.io\">VNST Whitepaper</a></li><li><a href=\"https://bscscan.com/token/0x3b26fb89eab263cc6cb1e91f611bae8793f927ef?ref=blog.vnst.io\">VNST Contract Address</a></li><li><a href=\"https://whitepaper.vnst.io/vnst_whitepaper_en/table-of-contents/legal-terms?ref=blog.vnst.io\">VNST Legal Framework</a></li></ul><p>We are excited about the opportunities and potential that VNST will bring in the future. Let's celebrate VNST's first Mint event and look forward to new milestones in our journey. Let's together create the future of cryptocurrency finance with VNST!</p><p>Thanks for your support!</p><blockquote>VNST team,<br>02-09-2023</blockquote><p><br></p>",
