      "id": "64ef1c4d259494d6157e728f",
      "uuid": "49a27bfc-1aee-4d4e-95fe-f6bdfee03d49",
      "title": "Stablecoin vs Fiat",
      "slug": "stablecoin-vs-fiat",
      "html": "<blockquote>In today's fast-paced and interconnected world, the evolution of digital currencies has sparked a growing interest in Stablecoin and their comparison to traditional fiat currency. Stablecoin, tethered to stable reserve assets like the US dollar, have gained prominence for their potential to reduce the volatility commonly associated with cryptocurrencies. In contrast, fiat currency, backed by governments, remains a widely accepted medium of exchange. As these two financial systems continue to coexist and shape the future of monetary transactions, understanding their unique characteristics becomes essential for anyone seeking to navigate the ever-changing landscape of modern finance.</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/08/Stable-coin---Fiat-Done-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/Stable-coin---Fiat-Done-1.png 600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/Stable-coin---Fiat-Done-1.png 1000w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/08/Stable-coin---Fiat-Done-1.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"definition\">Definition</h3><p><strong>Stablecoin</strong> are digital currencies that are linked to a “stable” reserve asset, such as the US dollar or other national currencies. Stablecoin, as opposed to unpegged cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin, are designed to reduce fluctuation risks.</p><p>Stablecoin prices are fixed to a reserve asset like the US dollar or other national currencies, Stablecoin serve as a link between cryptocurrency and daily fiat currency. When compared to Crypto currency, this reduces volatility dramatically, giving in a digital currency that is ideally equipped to anything from everyday transactions to cross-border transactions.</p><p><strong>A fiat currency</strong> is money that is backed by the government that issued it rather than a tangible commodity like gold. The majority of current currencies are fiat money, such as the US dollar, euro, pound, and yen. “An authoritative or arbitrary order” is what “Fiat” signifies.</p><p>The value of fiat money is determined by the supply and demand connection rather than the worth of the commodity used to create it.</p><p><strong>Features of Stable Coins:</strong></p><ul><li>Stablecoin are international, and accessible to everyone 24 /7. They transport data quickly, cheaply, and securely.</li><li>Stablecoin is adaptable and completely native.</li><li>Stablecoin customers only require a crypto wallet to transmit crypto to acquaintances in different nations; users do not even require several foreign bank accounts.</li><li>Authentic peer-to-peer transactions are feasible thanks to Stablecoin, which eliminates the necessity for third-party mediators to place orders.</li><li>Stablecoin like USDT, BUSD are a fast, secure and reliable alternative for transferring funds globally.</li><li>One of the major features is cheap/money saving. Stablecoin transferring reduces the standard cost banking fees, unwanted taxes, extras or other financial settlements.</li></ul><p><strong>Features Of Fiat Currency:</strong></p><ul><li>When a country is going through a difficult period, <strong>the government</strong> can control the supply of money to some extent. This empowers them to maintain, grow, or decrease the value of fiat currency.</li><li>The storage and management of fiat money is quite simple. If you already have Fiat money, you can either keep it at home or deposit it at a bank.</li><li>People may easily establish decisions and construct specialized business growth because of its capacity to store buying power. A company that makes mobile phones, for example, may invest in better technology, recruit and make payments, and reach fresh markets.</li><li>People may buy whatever items / products they choose using fiat currency instead of trading product for product, as was the case with barter commerce.</li></ul><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/08/stablecoin---fiat-Done.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"2532\" srcset=\"https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w600/2023/08/stablecoin---fiat-Done.png 600w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/size/w1000/2023/08/stablecoin---fiat-Done.png 1000w, https://blog.vnst.io/content/images/2023/08/stablecoin---fiat-Done.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p><strong>Stablecoin are the greatest option for</strong></p><ul><li>Conversion : You can convert/withdraw directly into fiat currencies.</li><li>Risk Free : Away from crypto obligations, as the Stablecoin like USDC are backed by trusted, verified organizations and undertake all the legal precautions.There are still risk of losing their Price Earnings to Growth, but the Issuer of the Stablecoin will have the actions to maintaining the price</li><li>Convenience : Transfer your funds among different blockchains and move liquidity between exchanges with ease and convenience .</li><li>Payments : Transfer business payments across the border and make settlements without needing any conversion or paying extras instantly.</li><li>Safe holding : Traders can use the stablecoin to hedge their trading assets to avoid fall in fluctuating market</li></ul><h2 id=\"conclusion\"><strong>Co</strong>nclusion</h2><p>In conclusion, Stablecoin and Fiat currency offer distinct benefits in the modern financial landscape. Stablecoin provides reduced volatility and efficient cross-border transactions, catering to the digital era's needs. Meanwhile, fiat currency's stability, widespread acceptance, and government backing make it a reliable medium of exchange. The coexistence of these two forms of currency presents diverse options for individuals and businesses.</p><p>Understanding their unique features empowers better decision-making, leveraging the advantages of each system effectively. As technology continues to shape finance, embracing both Stablecoin and fiat currency will play a pivotal role in driving the future of global transactions and economic interactions.</p><h2 id=\"about-vnst\">About VNST</h2><p>VNST is a decentralized stablecoin with transparent on-chain data, guaranteed by the stable value of the most popular and reputable stable coins in the global crypto asset market. The stablecoins that ensure value for VNST have transaction volume and stability proven over a long period of time, issued by reputable organizations with proven potential and periodically audited. VNST will be a safe, reliable solution, providing diverse and convenient choices and expanding future applications for users in the Web3 field in Vietnam and around the world.</p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/vnstcoin?ref=blog.vnst.io\">X</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VNST.io/\">Facebook </a>| <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstann?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Announcements</a> |  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/pwRwbcHHkK?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Discord</a> | <a href=\"https://t.me/vnstgroup?ref=blog.vnst.io\">Telegram Discussion</a></p>",
